Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,(beep)\N- Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- I am evacuating all\Ncitizens to the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare Manta Squad Omega, and dispatch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to every part of Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- But sir--\N- Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Citizens\Nof Atlas, please proceed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to the nearest underground\Nsubway station for shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dad? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- We need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Commander] We can't get the hard\Nlight shields back up, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The generators took too much damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Then don't\Nwaste resources on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Beta Squad, the creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Commander] We tried bombs, missiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't make a dent, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir, Schnee here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Penny is still MIA, but\Nwe've apprehended Arc,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiao-Long, and Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Stand by for further orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't let those\Nfugitives out of your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Still just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's where the Grimm took Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's even bigger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grimm don't take prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- This one did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you would just let us go--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Cease fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Manta squads, concentrate\Non secondary hostiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Command is working on a\Nsolution for the creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you have in mind, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] We aren't making any progress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,attacking the thing from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the inside,\Nit could be vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Science team is putting together a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's ready, we'll drop it off
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as close to the target as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, your team will deliver it on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending your rendezvous coordinates now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we will hold the point\Nand we will get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- But Oscar's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Hazel] That stunt you pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd have killed you if you didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just pop up somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you can make\Nthings easier on yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if you start telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've never wondered\Nwhy she recruited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You, specifically, to\Nhelp her find the relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- We share a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna create a new world order,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,no kingdoms and no Huntsmen Academies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- (chuckles) New world order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When Salem gets all four relics,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be no world left at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been alive longer\Nthan you can comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All she craves now is release.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop lying!\N(grunts)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Salem can't be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When she came for me, I killed\Nher over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The longest she was gone\Nwas only a few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,before she put herself back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I couldn't lift my arms anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,she showed me that, through her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have the vengeance I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, Hazel, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why she came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she could make you believe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is what you needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is what you deserve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, but Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Atlas, Remnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't done what\Nyou've done for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she pushed you to\Nthink it would help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now what
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,am I good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- How is she?\N- I've done what I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but she needs a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hopefully, May's able\Nto reach the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope they're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Salem's monster is making Grimm faster
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,than the Atlas military can kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The city won't stand a\Nchance unless we stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's massive. Way\Nbigger than a leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we even do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny launched Amity\Nand our message went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we just wait for someone to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they even come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] How did it all get like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fiona said your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't been heard from in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the last\Nthing they're worried about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is a couple of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I've got the ship\Nready to head back and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's chaos at the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas has its army,\Nbut Mantle only has us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,People are dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- People are dying here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have family in Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantle needed me, and to the Marigolds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that meant I wasn't their son anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I made sure that everyone knew
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wasn't their daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So forget 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got Henry, yours have Whitley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't know about--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which side are you on, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- We've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- There are no sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to help everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all facing Salem together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And together is the only way\Nwe're going to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, how exactly do we get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- "So long as this world turns,\Nyou shall walk its face."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the curse cast upon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Salem can divide\Nhumanity beyond repair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring all four relics back together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,she believes that maybe\Nher curse will be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods will rule against\Nus and destroy Remnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nice story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Gretchen's death\Ntaught me one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it was never to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Oscar] Please, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- But, Oscar--\N- You want 'em to trust us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Jinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want her to come out of the lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She can still answer one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that, you're just going
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to give Salem the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I'm giving you the password
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and hoping you'll find\Nthe truth for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Mercury] He's a prisoner, Em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll say what he thinks will get him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- So you're still going to Vacuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,after what I just told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Those are Salem's new orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know better than to disobey Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- But--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look, even if what he said was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't stop Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me yourself, Hazel tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He failed and he got in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Big guy's not going to\Npick fights he can't win,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither should we.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of this is pointless, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Salem's not ending the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- (laughing)\N[Tyrian] Of course she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Salem is destruction incarnate! (giggling)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mistress wishes to see the end of it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no ideal more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you couldn't see that from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you must be out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come along, Mr. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I have a date with the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can't blow it up\Nwith Oscar still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- That creature causes\Nmore damage every minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please, Winter, give us a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to rescue him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We could be your test run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what'll be\Nwaiting for you inside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can go ahead to check it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and look for Oscar while we're inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- You want to go inside that thing alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wouldn't you do it\Nfor Elm? Harriet? Vine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- We don't let feelings get in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of making the right call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Trading three lives for one is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do whatever it takes to find him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because we care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- (scoffs) I really had you\Npegged as the most level-headed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of the bunch, but I guess\Nyou're just as naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings don't matter, the job matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lose someone on\Nyour team, you move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace them, like Marrow replaced Tortuga
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and Winter replaced--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is replaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You are furious about losing Clover,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you, you miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't know anything about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you lost against Team RWBY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You, you try to fight how\Nyou feel about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll never truly work as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,(grunting)\N- Everyone, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We will drop you as close\Nas we can to the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fugitives and traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- I outrank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't out in\Ntime, we drop the payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't like this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you don't want to be\Na part of it at all anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know you don't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, what about Qrow and Robyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe if we get them out of wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they're being held, they could--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, see, you just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a situation\Nwhere everyone wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you all can come\Nwith me to help in Mantle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or I can drop you off\Nnear the front lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if you still want to help Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle and Robyn can't save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- (gasps) Klein!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miss Schnee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there was a patient\Nhere who needed my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- I, I am so sorry, Klein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault that Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please don't worry, my snowflake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It had nothing to do with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything to do with Jacques.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, that's sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, how did you know--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, young Whitley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you rang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,May I please see the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, she's in Weiss's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go up the--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- I haven't been gone\Nthat long, Master Whitley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- You called Klein?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- That girl needs a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it means so much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm, I'm sorry.
